        "des": "{\"spoken_languages\":\"English\",\"rooms\":\"Make yourself at home in one of the 5 guestrooms featuring microwaves. Prepare your meals in the shared/communal kitchen. Complimentary wired and wireless internet access is available. Bathrooms have shower/tub combinations and slippers.\",\"onsite_payments\":\"Debit cards not accepted, Cash\",\"dining\":\"Grab a bite to eat at one of the hotel's many dining establishments, which include 2 restaurants and 2 coffee shops/cafes. Mingle with other guests at the complimentary reception, held daily.\",\"business_amenities\":\"Featured amenities include a 24-hour front desk and coffee/tea in a common area.\",\"location\":\"With a stay at Royce Youth Hostel , you'll be centrally located in Sharjah, within a 15-minute drive of Dubai Creek and City Centre Deira.  This hotel is 9.9 mi (16 km) from Gold Souk and 11.6 mi (18.7 km) from Dubai World Trade Centre.\",\"attractions\":\"Distances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer.  Sharjah Mega Mall - 0.8 km / 0.5 mi  King Faisal Mosque - 1 km / 0.6 mi  Al Noor Mosque - 1.5 km / 0.9 mi  Sharjah Gold Souq - 1.5 km / 0.9 mi  Sharjah Gold Center - 1.6 km / 1 mi  Khalid Lake - 1.6 km / 1 mi  Al Noor Island - 1.9 km / 1.2 mi  Al Jazeera Park - 2.4 km / 1.5 mi  Al Majaz Waterfront - 2.4 km / 1.5 mi  Rolla Mall - 2.5 km / 1.5 mi  Al Qasba - 3.7 km / 2.3 mi  Sharjah Cricket Stadium - 3.9 km / 2.4 mi  Corniche Mosque - 4 km / 2.5 mi  Sharjah City Centre - 4.7 km / 2.9 mi  Expo Centre Sharjah - 5.6 km / 3.5 mi  The nearest airports are:Dubai Intl. Airport (DXB) - 15.4 km / 9.6 mi Sharjah (SHJ-Sharjah Intl.) - 16.7 km / 10.4 mi \",\"headline\":\"In Sharjah (Al Qasimia)\"}",
